    {
      "id": 301,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 9,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 20
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "<div style=\"padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center; font-family: monospace;\">\n\n<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-around; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">\n  <span style=\"padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 4px; background: rgba(138, 184, 255, 0.15); color: #8AB8FF; border: 1px solid #8AB8FF;\">Metrics</span>\n  <span style=\"padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 4px; background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.15); color: #A78BFA; border: 1px solid #A78BFA;\">Logs</span>\n  <span style=\"padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 4px; background: rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.15); color: #F472B6; border: 1px solid #F472B6;\">Traces</span>\n  <span style=\"padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 4px; background: rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.15); color: #FB923C; border: 1px solid #FB923C;\">Profiles</span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 2em; color: #F472B6; margin: 0.5rem 0;\">&darr;</div>\n\n<div>\n  <span style=\"padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(252, 165, 165, 0.2); color: #FCA5A5; border: 2px solid #FCA5A5; font-weight: bold;\">Conversations</span>\n</div>\n\n<p style=\"color: #9ca3af; font-size: 0.9em; margin-top: 1.5rem; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\nMetrics, logs, traces, profiles. The four classical signals of OpenTelemetry. The fifth signal, conversations, branches from traces.\n</p>\n\n</div>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 400,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "\ud83e\uddf6 The singularity. From any conversation, walk down to the SQL that broke.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 29
      },
